name: KCCPAD
description:
KCCPad is the first major launch pad on KCC. KCCPad brings stabilty, safety and amazing opportunities on the new and highly anticipated KuCoin Community Chain!

The KCC launch pad is a deflationary launch pad with a 1% fee for selling, a 25% fee for early unstaking and projects will need to commit to buying and burning KCC tokens to launch their IDO.
